    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so annoying how much it eats into my payment. it feels like there are these little hidden costs or something just eating away at the money before i even get a chance to pay off the actual loan. are there any other factors that can make it feel like the interest is working against me more than it should?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
